display_long_description:
# Defend your tower, monkey-style – in VR!

Dive into exciting VR tower defense gameplay, where you control a monkey defending its land, throwing stones and using explosive tools to take down waves of enemies in each challenging level.
[media]

Get ready for a thrilling VR battle where your monkey must defend its territory by using a mix of stone-throwing, explosive mines, and double-barrel shots against relentless waves of foes.
[media]

Engage in action-packed VR combat, using bomb mines and a double-barrel gun to blast through increasingly tough waves of invaders in this intense tower defense game.
[media]

A fast-paced tower defense VR game where you use precision stone-throwing to fend off waves of approaching enemies, combining quick reflexes and strategic defense.
[media]
